<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="ideedf6ffe-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="ideedf6fff-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—Par. (1). <ref href="/us/pl/107/171">Pub. L. 107–171</ref> inserted hyphen after “means”, designated remainder of existing provisions as subpar. (A), substituted “; and” for period at end, and added subpar. (B).</p>
</note>
